acceptance_criteria:
Epic is done when the three child beads land and end-to-end `bugbot design-sandbox` on a repo:
- (a) detects build systems + mines the repo's env artifacts;
- (b) emits a concrete sandbox: block (image, dep_strategy, network, resources, setup_cmds, and local_mounts when monorepo/local-path deps are detected -- the last gated on bugbot-ixu);
- (c) smoke-tests the candidate under network=none and reports pass / env_error with category;
- (d) writes/merges into bugbot.yaml ONLY with --write (proposal + diff otherwise); the edge-case agent tier is gated behind --agent.
